{"Body":["Dear Applicant,"," ","Thank you for your interest in a full-time position at Trilegal. As part of our application process and in order to assess technical ability, we request that you log into the following link and complete a minimum of five assessments over the next seven days. Completing more than the minimum required is likely to give you a performance advantage."," ","Please access http://higherknowledge.in/go/trilegal within 24 hours of receiving this mail, and follow the instructions. Click the “continue” button to get your first assessment. Once you submit the answer, you will get the next one. The seven days’ time given, is inclusive of the day of login. ","","<strong>Your performance on the assessments will be one of the factors taken into account, when considering you for a position with us."," </strong>","Once you are logged in, ensure you upload your CV. Also mention your contact details, College, preferred location, and start date. You can insert these details at the top right of the web page, just under your name. ","","<strong>We will be unable to process your application if you do not fill in these details. </strong>","","Those who successfully complete this assessment may be invited to attend an additional round of interviews/discussions. Please note that completing this assessment successfully does NOT indicate that you have been successful in your application. It is only the first step in our assessment process.","","All the best!","","Regards,","","Trilegal","","Please note: Do not reply to this message as emails sent to this address are not monitored. ",""],"CC":"","Subject":"Your Application to Trilegal"}
